feature: [FASHION DESIGN & LIGHTWEIGHT] - Built with metal casing for high-end and fashion look, the newly launched SoundPEATS Q34 Bluetooth headphones are still super lightweight at only 0.60oz for your easy carrying.

[BLUETOOTH 4.1 + APTX] - Come with Bluetooth 4.1 and aptX codec technology to ensure smooth Bluetooth transmission and high fidelity sound. The headphones are widely compatible with most Bluetooth-enabled devices, both Android and iOS.
[STRONG BUILT-IN MAGNETS] - Built-in stronger magnets stick both earbuds together like a necklace around your neck for your better storage when not in use and keep you away from tangled wire.

[BLUETOOTH 4.1 + APTX] - Come with Bluetooth 4.1 and aptX codec technology to ensure smooth Bluetooth transmission and high fidelity sound. The headphones are widely compatible with most Bluetooth-enabled devices, both Android and iOS.
[STRONG BUILT-IN MAGNETS] - Built-in stronger magnets stick both earbuds together like a necklace around your neck for your better storage when not in use and keep you away from tangled wire.

[SECURE & COMFORTABLE FIT] - Ergonomically built with oblique angle in-ear design, along with soft different sized ear tips and hooks to fit your ears better and reduce ambient noise, all for your snug and comfortable wearing and enjoyment.

[IN-LINE MIC & VOLUME CONTROL] - With compact and exquisite in-line control, the headphones enable you to make hands-free calls and manage music easily and instantly. Tips: When charging with a charging adapter, please make sure the current should not be greater than 1A. SoundPEATS provides 12 months hassle-free warranty to ensure the enjoyment of your purchase.
